title: Hour 3 - Al Michaels, Dan Le Batard
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Al Michaels, Dan Le Batard
description:
Dan talks with legendary broadcaster Al Michaels to reflect on the incredible life and legacy of Vin Scully. Dan Le Batard stops by to react to the Miami Dolphins and Tom Brady tampering scandal.
